Class C_ConvertGeographicCoordinates

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.converters.C_ConvertGeographicCoordinates
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    I_ConstantString
    public class C_ConvertGeographicCoordinates
extends java.lang.Object
implements I_ConstantString
    Utility to convert from geographic coordinates to meters and compute distances in meter from the raster origin?
    Calculation depends on the raster used
    Author:
    author Moussa Sall, oct.2015
    source: http://geodesie.ign.fr/contenu/fichiers/documentation/pedagogiques/TransformationsCoordonneesGeodesiques.pdf
